videos.description: Brady Manek swats down Kendall Smith's block to shut down Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Manek gets chase down block for Sooners

videos.description: Trae Young  breaks down the court and finishes with the lay-in to extend Oklahoma's lead.
videos.headline: Young scores on smooth layup

videos.description: Trae Young finds Jamuni McNeace under the basket and he finishes with a slam for the Sooners.
videos.headline: Young sets up McNeace dunk

videos.description: Travarius Shine steals a pass then slams it down on the other end to cut the Sooners' lead.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State answers with steal and slam

videos.description: Trae Young drives down the court and throws a quick pass to Jamuni McNeace who throws it down for Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Young and McNeace strike again with alley-oop

videos.description: Trae Young finds Kendall Smith down low and he elevates for another Sooners' dunk.
videos.headline: Young finds Lattin for another Sooners slam

videos.description: Brady Manek sinks a corner three to give him five from behind the arc against Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Manek stays hot behind the arc with corner 3-pointer

videos.description: Trae Young nearly gets a triple-double with 27 points, 10 assists and 9 rebounds in Oklahoma's win against rival Oklahoma State.
